<doc id="1310428" wikidata="Q7867227" url="?curid=1310428" title="USS Alligator">
<text>USS &quot;Alligator&quot; may refer to the following ships operated by the United States Navy:

* was a schooner built in 1809 as &quot;Gunboat No. 166&quot; and named &quot;Alligator&quot; in 1812
* was a sloop purchased in 1813. The British captured her on 14 December 1814 during the Battle of Lake Borgne.
* was a schooner, launched in 1820, and scuttled in 1822
* was a non-commissioned submarine launched in 1862 and sank in April 1863.</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q11220" start="75" end="93" title="United States Navy" label="United States Navy"/>
